text: OUA or Oua may refer to: ==Organisations== * Open Universities Australia, an online higher education organization based in Australia * Organisation of African Unity, now replaced by the African Union * Ontario University Athletics, a regional membership association for Canadian universities ==Places== * Oua, an island in Tuvalu * 'O'ua, an island in Tonga * Ouagadougou Airport (IATA code)
title: OUA
